.SH NAME
SDL_qsort_r \- Sort an array, passing a userdata pointer to the compare function\[char46]
.SH HEADER FILE
Defined in SDL3/SDL_stdinc\[char46]h

.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #include \(dqSDL3/SDL.h\(dq
